│ """""""""                                                                                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ The '``llvm.uadd.sat``' family of intrinsic functions perform unsigned                                                                                                                                            │
│ saturating addition on the 2 arguments.                                                                                                                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ Arguments                                                                                                                                                                                                         │
